org.cpsolver.studentsct.online

Class OnlineReservation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.reservation.Reservation
        • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.OnlineReservation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Reservation>, AssignmentComparable<Reservation,Request,Enrollment>, CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>

    public class OnlineReservation
extends Reservation
    An online reservation. A simple class modeling any reservation of a student. This class is particularly useful when a model containing only the given student is constructed (to provide him/her with a schedule or suggestions).
    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
